  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 180&deg;C/ 160&deg;C (fan)/ 400&deg;F/ Gas 6</p>\r\n<p>Boil a kettle&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Strip the<strong> rosemary leaves</strong> from the stalks and chop them finely</p>\r\n<p>Peel and chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p>\r\n<p>Add them to a pot of <strong>salted</strong> <strong>boiled water</strong>, bring to the boil&nbsp;over a high heat and cook for 10-15 min or until just cooked (known as parboiling)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Meanwhile, lay a sheet of<strong> tin</strong>&nbsp;<strong>foil</strong> onto a baking tray&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Place your hand flat over the <strong>chicken breast<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> on a chopping board</p>\r\n<p>Slice in half as if you were cutting a burger bun, so you are left with 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> thinner pieces</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>sliced chicken</strong> to the foil&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>honey</strong>, <strong>Dijon mustard</strong>, <strong>chopped&nbsp;garlic</strong>, zest and juice of the <strong>lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>, 1-2 tsp <strong>pepper</strong> (freshly ground is best!) and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>&ndash;&nbsp;this is your <strong>lemon marinade&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Spoon the <strong>lemon marinade</strong> over the <strong>chicken</strong> and scrunch the edges of the <strong>foil</strong> around the chicken (to stop it spilling out), leaving the parcel open</p>\r\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for 15 min</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the parboiled <strong>potatoes</strong> and leave them to steam-dry&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>butter</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once the <strong>butter</strong> has melted, add the <strong>potatoes</strong> with the<strong> chopped&nbsp;rosemary</strong> and a big pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-5 min or until they're just starting to crisp &ndash; these are your<strong>&nbsp;saut&eacute;ed potatoes</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has had an initial 15 min, add the <strong>saut&eacute;ed&nbsp;</strong><strong>potatoes </strong>to the same tray and return the tray to the oven for 5 min, or until the <strong>chicken</strong> is cooked through</p>\r\n<p>Meanwhile, wash and dry the <strong>baby&nbsp;leaf salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/713.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the cooked <strong>lemon pepper&nbsp;</strong><strong>chicken</strong> with the <strong>saut&eacute;ed potatoes</strong> and <strong>baby leaf</strong><strong><strong>&nbsp;s</strong>alad</strong> to the side</p>\r\n<p>Spoon the remaining <strong>lemon marinade</strong>&nbsp;over the chicken&nbsp;and salad</p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 8,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
